Main Steps in the Project:


Look at the Big Picture.(understand the problem)
Get the Data. ( public repositorires, /meta Portals)
Discover and vidualize the data to gain insights. ( visulaization and corelation)
Prepare Data for Machine Learning.(cleansing) 
Select a model.
Fine-tune your model. (training and testing)
Present your solution. 
Launch, Monitor and maintain your system.


